            <span class="text-red-400 font-semibold">You found a critical bug.</span> Your users are frustrated. App store review takes 1-2 weeks. 
            Your 5-star rating drops every day you wait.
          </p>
          
          <div class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-3xl">
            <div class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-700">
